T1  - TESTING FOR MULTIPLE BUBBLES: LIMIT THEORY OF REAL-TIME DETECTORS
AU  - Phillips, Peter C. B.
AU  - Shi, Shuping
AU  - Yu, Jun
Y1  - 2015/11/01
PY  - 2015
DA  - 2015/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12131
